WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   WNEWS RGL
</CO>
<LP>
   REGAL INTERNATIONAL Inc. (Houston) -- Vijay Dandapani was
elected a director of this energy industry products maker.
Mr. Dandapani is president of Zurich Corp., an investment
concern and major investor in Regal. He succeeds George
Moore, who resigned from the board last Tuesday for
unspecified reasons.
